00:58:38.240 --> 00:58:43.660
He has published on topics such
as the history and heritage

00:58:43.660 --> 00:58:46.610
of 19th century astronomy,

00:58:46.610 --> 00:58:50.580
the history of colonial
observatories

00:58:50.580 --> 00:58:56.700
and the circulation of knowledge
in 18th century Europe.

00:58:56.700 --> 00:59:00.340
Raposo is responsible
for the use and research

00:59:00.340 --> 00:59:05.200
of the Adler Planetarium's
