02:10:41.670 --> 02:10:43.140
Oh, wow! All right.

02:10:43.140 --> 02:10:44.970
It must be the field
that you're all in.

02:10:44.970 --> 02:10:46.270
You're correct [laughter].

02:10:46.270 --> 02:10:51.920
So the image on the far bottom
right is a quasar 3C273,

02:10:51.920 --> 02:10:55.330
incredibly distant,
billions of light years away,

02:10:55.330 --> 02:11:00.680
powered by this massive, super
