of high energy particles.

02:11:05.060 --> 02:11:06.730
It's gargantuan.

02:11:06.730 --> 02:11:11.350
And the image right
next to is -- oh, me --

02:11:11.350 --> 02:11:12.650
which one is that one?

02:11:12.650 --> 02:11:15.230
That one is not my image.

02:11:15.230 --> 02:11:16.730
It is membrane fission.

